OL,3,CPaddleboard company owner loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge sentence over fatal tour
OL,6,FA former police officer who ran a
OL,7,Fpaddleboarding company has lost a
OL,8,FCourt of Appeal bid to challenge her
OL,9,Fprison sentence after four people
OL,10,Fdrowned during an excursion on a river
OL,11,Fin south-west Wales.
OL,13,FNerys Lloyd, 41, led a stand-up
OL,14,Fpaddleboarding tour on the River
OL,15,FCleddau in Haverfordwest,
OL,16,FPembrokeshire, in October 2021 despite
OL,17,F"extremely hazardous conditions", with
OL,18,Fweather warnings in place.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@`O]
