OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1780675876
OL,3,CPaddleboard company owner loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge sentence over fatal tour
OL,6,FLloyd was sentenced to 10 years and
OL,7,Fsix months in April 2025 for four
OL,8,Fcounts of gross negligence
OL,9,Fmanslaughter and one offence under the
OL,10,FHealth and Safety at Work Act.
OL,12,FPaul O'Dwyer, 42, Andrea Powell, 41,
OL,13,FMorgan Rogers, 24, and Nicola
OL,14,FWheatley, 40, all died as they were
OL,15,Fswept over, becoming trapped under the
OL,16,Ffast-moving water.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
