PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1780675876
OL,3,CPaddleboard company owner loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge sentence over fatal tour
OL,6,FSwansea Crown Court previously heard
OL,7,FLloyd - who was the owner and sole
OL,8,Fdirector of Salty Dog Co Ltd, which
OL,9,Forganised the tour - failed to warn
OL,10,Fthe group about a dangerous weir with
OL,11,Fa 1.3m drop along the route, or how to
OL,12,Fnavigate it.
OL,14,FAt the Court of Appeal on Friday, June
OL,15,F5 2026, lawyers for Lloyd made a bid
OL,16,Fto bring an appeal against her
OL,17,Fsentence.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
