OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1780675876
OL,3,CPaddleboard company owner loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge sentence over fatal tour
OL,6,FDavid Elias KC, for Lloyd, said the
OL,7,Fjudge should have reduced the starting
OL,8,Fpoint for how the sentence would be
OL,9,Fcalculated.
OL,11,FHe said: "There were very significant
OL,12,Fand powerful mitigating factors that
OL,13,Fwe say should have led the judge to
OL,14,Freduce the eight-year starting point
OL,15,Fto less than seven."
OL,26,@sD@JOUwD@TO]
