OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1780675876
OL,3,CPaddleboard company owner loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge sentence over fatal tour
OL,6,FThe barrister later said there was
OL,7,F"far too great a leap" when the judge
OL,8,Fincreased the sentence to 15 years to
OL,9,Freflect the four deaths, before the
OL,10,Fterm was reduced to factor in Lloyd's
OL,11,Fguilty pleas.
OL,13,FHowever, Lady Justice May, Mr Justice
OL,14,FMartin Spencer and Judge Martin Picton
OL,15,Frefused the bid to bring an appeal.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@VO]
