OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1780675876
OL,3,CPaddleboard company owner loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge sentence over fatal tour
OL,6,FLady Justice May said: "It is not
OL,7,Farguable that a sentence of 10 years
OL,8,Fand six months was manifestly
OL,9,Fexcessive," adding the sentencing
OL,10,Fjudge "clearly had all the mitigating
OL,11,Ffeatures in mind".
OL,13,FAt Lloyd's sentencing in April 2025
OL,14,FJudge Mrs Justice Stacey said there
OL,15,Fwere Met Office weather warnings at
OL,16,Fthe time of the incident, as well as a
OL,17,Fflood alert in place through Natural
OL,18,FResources Wales.
