OL,3,CPaddleboard company owner loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge sentence over fatal tour
OL,6,FShe told Lloyd that she had watched
OL,7,FCCTV footage of the incident, which
OL,8,Fshe described as "too distressing" to
OL,9,Fplay in court.
OL,11,FA conversation between Lloyd and her
OL,12,Fwife was inadvertently recorded on her
OL,13,Fphone hours after the incident.
OL,15,FShe could be heard saying she was
OL,16,F"finished" and the incident was "100%"
OL,17,Fher fault, but blamed Mr O'Dwyer in
OL,18,Fthe aftermath of the incident.
