OL,3,CPaddleboard company owner loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge sentence over fatal tour
OL,6,FMrs Justice Stacey told the court that
OL,7,Fthe four people who died had been "cut
OL,8,Foff in their prime, with so much to
OL,9,Flive for and look forward to."
OL,11,FShe told the defendant: "There was no
OL,12,Fsafety briefing beforehand.
OL,14,F"None of the participants had the
OL,15,Fright type of leash for their board,
OL,16,Fand you didn't have any next of kin
OL,17,Fdetails.
